  The SEO Reality Check Every Next.js Developer Needs
  
  You’ve built a lightning-fast Next.js app with a beautiful UI and flawless functionality. The deployment pipeline is smooth, the code is clean, and users love the experience but there’s one big issue: Google can’t find you.
  
  After years of building applications, I’ve seen many projects fail not because of poor code, but because of overlooked SEO. Modern frameworks like **Next.js 15+** have changed how search engines read and rank content. In this guide, we’ll cut through the confusion and show you exactly how to implement SEO in Next.js from meta tags to structured data so your app doesn’t just run well, it also gets discovered.
  
