  ## The Technical Foundation: How SEO Works in Modern React Applications
  
  Understanding the Crawling Challenge
  
  Traditional server-rendered websites serve complete HTML documents with all content immediately visible to search engine crawlers. Single Page Applications (SPAs) broke this model by rendering content client-side through JavaScript, creating what SEO experts call the “crawling gap.”
  
